description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured a new side of Denise and a pizza party! For the Real Housewives of New York recap, QIL Gillian Jacobs (Community) joins Danny. The RHONY women are still in Mexico and flirting their way through the rest of the trip.

See Gillian's new movie, I Used To Go Here, OnDemand NOW!


Gillian RHONY Recap: 24:21ish


Watch the interview with Gillian on YouTube at YouTube.com/DannyPellegrino1
